$ Calling the Windows API from VBA

In order to call the Windows API from → development/languages/VBA[Visual Basic for Applications] (VBA), the respective API functions and memory structures must be defined
in VBA. After that declaration, the API can be accessed. Some → development/languages/VBA/Win-API/examples[examples] are here.

The following code snippet shows some declarations for a few interesting functions:

gh|WinAPI-4-VBA|/WinAPI.bas||
